BEGIN_SILENCE EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL /tmp/tainted.txt SEND_VAL r DO_FCALL fopen EXT_FCALL_END END_SILENCE ASSIGN EXT_STMT JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL fgets EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN  JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL fclose EXT_FCALL_END JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL filter_var EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL filter_var EXT_FCALL_END JMPZ ASSIGN JMP ASSIGN  EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT * FROM COURSE c WHERE c.id IN (SELECT idcourse FROM REGISTRATION WHERE idstudent='%s') SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END 
BEGIN_SILENCE EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL /tmp/tainted.txt SEND_VAL r DO_FCALL fopen EXT_FCALL_END END_SILENCE ASSIGN EXT_STMT JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL fgets EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN  JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL fclose EXT_FCALL_END JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL filter_var EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL filter_var EXT_FCALL_END JMPZ ASSIGN JMP ASSIGN  EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT Trim(a.FirstName) & ' ' & Trim(a.LastName) AS employee_name, a.city, a.street & (' '  a.housenum) AS address FROM Employees AS a  WHERE a.supervisor=%u SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END

BEGIN_SILENCE EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL /tmp/tainted.txt SEND_VAL r DO_FCALL fopen EXT_FCALL_END END_SILENCE ASSIGN EXT_STMT JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL fgets EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN  JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL fclose EXT_FCALL_END JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT ASSIGN_ADD EXT_STMT ADD_STRING SELECT Trim(a.FirstName) & ' ' & Trim(a.LastName) AS employee_name, a.city, a.street & (' '  a.housenum) AS address FROM Employees AS a  WHERE a.supervisor=  ADD_VAR ADD_CHAR ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END

BEGIN_SILENCE EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL /tmp/tainted.txt SEND_VAL r DO_FCALL fopen EXT_FCALL_END END_SILENCE ASSIGN EXT_STMT JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL fgets EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN  JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL fclose EXT_FCALL_END JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT INIT_ARRAY safe1 ADD_ARRAY_ELEMENT safe2 ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL in_array EXT_FCALL_END JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN JMP EXT_STMT FETCH_DIM_R ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT Trim(a.FirstName) & ' ' & Trim(a.LastName) AS employee_name, a.city, a.street & (' '  a.housenum) AS address FROM Employees AS a  WHERE a.supervisor=%d SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END 
BEGIN_SILENCE EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL /tmp/tainted.txt SEND_VAL r DO_FCALL fopen EXT_FCALL_END END_SILENCE ASSIGN EXT_STMT JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL fgets EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN  JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL fclose EXT_FCALL_END JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT NOP EXT_STMT FETCH_CLASS Sanitize EXT_FCALL_BEGIN NEW DO_FCALL_BY_NAME EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT INIT_METHOD_CALL sanitize EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL_BY_NAME EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT * FROM '%s' SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT RETURN EXT_NOP RECV EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_real_escape_string EXT_FCALL_END RETURN 
FETCH_R _GET FETCH_DIM_R UserData ASSIGN EXT_STMT ASSIGN /^[a-zA-Z]*$/ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAR DO_FCALL preg_match EXT_FCALL_END IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT CONCAT SELECT * FROM ' CONCAT ' ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END

FETCH_R _GET FETCH_DIM_R UserData ASSIGN EXT_STMT INIT_ARRAY safe1 ADD_ARRAY_ELEMENT safe2 ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL in_array EXT_FCALL_END JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN JMP EXT_STMT FETCH_DIM_R ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT Trim(a.FirstName) & ' ' & Trim(a.LastName) AS employee_name, a.city, a.street & (' '  a.housenum) AS address FROM Employees AS a  WHERE a.supervisor=%d SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END 
FETCH_R _GET FETCH_DIM_R UserData ASSIGN EXT_STMT NOP EXT_STMT FETCH_CLASS Sanitize EXT_FCALL_BEGIN NEW DO_FCALL_BY_NAME EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT INIT_METHOD_CALL sanitize EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL_BY_NAME EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT * FROM '%s' SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT RETURN EXT_NOP RECV EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_real_escape_string EXT_FCALL_END RETURN

EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL /bin/cat /tmp/tainted.txt SEND_VAL r DO_FCALL popen EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL fread EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL pclose EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT INIT_ARRAY safe1 ADD_ARRAY_ELEMENT safe2 ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL in_array EXT_FCALL_END JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN JMP EXT_STMT FETCH_DIM_R ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT Trim(a.FirstName) & ' ' & Trim(a.LastName) AS employee_name, a.city, a.street & (' '  a.housenum) AS address FROM Employees AS a  WHERE a.supervisor=%d SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END 
EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL /bin/cat /tmp/tainted.txt SEND_VAL r DO_FCALL popen EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL fread EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL pclose EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT NOP EXT_STMT FETCH_CLASS Sanitize EXT_FCALL_BEGIN NEW DO_FCALL_BY_NAME EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT INIT_METHOD_CALL sanitize EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL_BY_NAME EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT * FROM '%s' SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT RETURN EXT_NOP RECV EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_real_escape_string EXT_FCALL_END RETURN 
FETCH_R _POST FETCH_DIM_R UserData ASSIGN EXT_STMT ASSIGN /^[a-zA-Z]*$/ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAR DO_FCALL preg_match EXT_FCALL_END IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT CONCAT SELECT * FROM ' CONCAT ' ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END

EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL ls SEND_REF DO_FCALL system EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT ASSIGN /^[a-zA-Z]*$/ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAR DO_FCALL preg_match EXT_FCALL_END IS_EQUAL JMPZ EXT_STMT ASSIGN JMP EXT_STMT ASSIGN  EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT lastname, firstname FROM drivers, vehicles WHERE drivers.id = vehicles.ownerid AND vehicles.tag='%s' SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END

INIT_ARRAY ASSIGN EXT_STMT ASSIGN_DIM OP_DATA safe EXT_STMT FETCH_R _GET FETCH_DIM_R userData ASSIGN_DIM OP_DATA EXT_STMT ASSIGN_DIM OP_DATA safe EXT_STMT FETCH_DIM_R ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL filter_var EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR SEND_VAL DO_FCALL filter_var EXT_FCALL_END JMPZ ASSIGN JMP ASSIGN  EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL SELECT Trim(a.FirstName) & ' ' & Trim(a.LastName) AS employee_name, a.city, a.street & (' '  a.housenum) AS address FROM Employees AS a  WHERE a.supervisor='%u' SEND_VAR DO_FCALL sprintf EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL localhost SEND_VAL mysql_user SEND_VAL mysql_password DO_FCALL mysql_connect EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAL dbname DO_FCALL mysql_select_db EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT CONCAT query :  CONCAT <br /><br /> ECHO EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_query EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_fetch_array EXT_FCALL_END ASSIGN JMPZ EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL print_r EXT_FCALL_END EXT_STMT ECHO <br /> JMP EXT_STMT EXT_FCALL_BEGIN SEND_VAR DO_FCALL mysql_close EXT_FCALL_END
